com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.core

Class IncrementalStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.core.PersistentStore
      • com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.core.IncrementalStore
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AndroidSqlPersistentStore

    public abstract class IncrementalStore
extends PersistentStore
    An IncrementalStore represents a persistence store in which data is loaded or saved incrementally as needed. It is typically used when the entire data set cannot fit in-memory, and must be "paged-in" into memory on-demand. This is an abstract class that can be implemented to provide support for such persistence stores.
